      "acceptanceCriteria": "Hemolysis constitutive model selection must be justified through sensitivity analysis across candidate power-law models; model-form uncertainty must be quantified and propagated to QOI.",
      "rationale": "Single Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model used without sensitivity analysis across alternative formulations; model-form uncertainty is acknowledged but not quantified. Achieved level 2 versus required level 5."
