    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the breadth of validation activities collectively support a High assurance level for the hemolysis predictions. Individual factor gaps were judged to be compensated by the overall rigor of the UQ framework and the conservative nature of the hemolysis model. The submission is accepted for regulatory submission.",
